        "content": "Great! Let's dive into the topic of the water cycle and its connection to climate change. We'll explore how these systems interact and impact our environment. \n\nLet's start with a fundamental question. Sarah, can you explain the steps of the water cycle and how water moves through the environment?\n\n---\n\nOnce Sarah responds, provide feedback and ask another student a related question.",
